      <hedline>
        <hl1>Introduction</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Reader responses to articles on hot new black comedians, TV's Survivor program and Nelson Aldrich's airing of family laundry (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The very different styles of two hot comedians, Chris Tucker and Chris Rock, sparked debate on ''blackness'' and audience appeal. Many readers connected Sandy Weill's deft elimination of competition to TV's ''Survivor.'' And Nelson Aldrich's airing of family laundry drew comment.</p>
      </block>
